Santonudhar.com Santonu Dhar Facebook Santonu Kumar Dhar also known as Santonu Dhar is an independent film maker and businessman. [1] He is the founder, and former Editor-In-Chief of Haule Haule Magazine (ISSN: 2078 - 8797).[2] He was born into a Bengali Kayashta family on June 16, 1987 in Bangladesh. [3]Santonu Dhar has authored also several books.[4] He has started working on a biographical film based on the life of Mohandas Karamchand Gandhi. He started his film making career with a Bengali and English language film based on biographic life history of an young Indian freedom fighter[5] In May 2012, Santonu Dhar launched Santonu Dhar Foundation with an aim to help poor people with financial aid for education, health and others.[6]
